            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/fremont-man-who-illegally-smuggled-headlights-for-years-gets-18-month-prison-sentence">
                Fremont man who illegally smuggled headlights for years gets 18 month prison sentence
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              A man who pleaded guilty to running a long-running, vehicle headlight smuggling operation in the Bay Area was sentenced Friday to 18 months in prison.
             </p>
             <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-21T15:49:02-07:00">
              2 hours ago
             </time>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/police-chief-says-miami-partying-couldnt-go-on-any-longer">
                Police chief says Miami partying "couldn't go on any longer"
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              Pointing to over 1,000 arrests, Miami Beach officials warned Sunday that the unruly spring break crowd gathering by the thousands, fighting, destroying property and refusing to wear masks has become a serious threat to public safety.
             </p>
             <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-21T17:32:13-07:00">
              26 mins ago
             </time>

            </div>

               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
